## DESIGN PATTERNS OBSERVED\
\
1. All entities use:\
   - UUID `id`\
   - Audit fields:\
     - createdAt / createdBy\
     - lastModifiedAt / lastModifiedBy\
\
2. Reference/config entities use:\
   - `isActive`\
   - `sortOrder`\
\
3. Transitional compatibility pattern:\
   - Expense stores both raw strings and relational references\
   - Booking stores both `propertyName` and `propertyRef`\
\
4. Relationship naming convention:\
   - To-One references use `...Ref`\
   - To-Many inverses use plural names\
