## CURRENT MIGRATION DIRECTION\
\
### Goal\
Move properties and bookings from prototype / JSON-backed flows into Core Data so Bookings, Calendar, and related screens can reference them relationally.\
\
### Transitional approach\
- Keep `propertyName` on Booking for compatibility during migration\
- Use `propertyRef` as the relational source of truth moving forward\
